---
title: Yellow Thai Style Veggie Noodles with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Peanuts
description: Turmeric in combination with red chillies help make Thai Yellow different from the other colours of spice pastes in Thai cuisine, resulting in a milder flavour. Here, our Thai Yellow Style Veggie Noodles hero the veg.
